descriptions.description:
All primary data files of measurements and processed data of the journal article mentioned under related publications from the Buchmeiser group and the Copéret gropup can be found here. &lt;br/&gt;
The data consist of:&lt;br/&gt;
*Processed (mestrenova) and unprocessed (fid-files) NMR spectra of molecular compunds&lt;br/&gt;
*FT-IR spectra&lt;br/&gt;
*Catalysis data (excel sheets)&lt;br/&gt;
*Data for calculating the catalyst loading on the silica&lt;br/&gt;
*Solid state NMR spectra of the immobilized catalyst
